Package org.opengis.cite.iso19142

Class WFS2

java.lang.Object
org.opengis.cite.iso19142.WFS2
public class WFS2 extends Object
Contains various constants pertaining to WFS 2.0 service interfaces as specified in ISO 19142:2010 and related standards.
See Also:
  • "ISO 19142:2010, Geographic information -- Web Feature Service"
